ZO_CreateStringId("MSAL_JUNK_THRESHOLD_TOOLTIP","Only available when |ccc922f<<2>>|r is set to |ccc922f<<1>>|r.\n\nAmong items discarded to the disposer, items with value at or above the threshold will be marked as junk, while those below will be destroyed. When set to 0, no items will be destroyed.\n\nItems that have their own <<1>> option are not affected by this setting")
