ZO_CreateStringId("MSAL_INTRICATE_DECON_TOOLTIP","When set to |ccc922f<<1>>|r, looted items will be auto selected into the decon slot upon your next visit to a crafting station or decon assistant\n\nOnly activates when the corresponding |ccc922fcrafting skill line has NOT reached level 50|r. Items with maxed skill lines will no longer be registered for deconstruction")
